game.name: Math Test 2
game.description:
What a fabulous math test quiz we have brought to you today! Are you ready to become the part of it and put your algebra and quick thinking abilities to the test? Join Math Test 2 and be prepared to complete the different mathematical operations! You would have a very short time to handle multiple arithmetical operations. Completing task in the specified time limit would definitely make your job pretty challenging and tough. Unleash the left side of your brain and answer questions as fast as you can to score higher!

Here you would get a chance to deal with multiple mathematical operations, including subtraction, addition and multiplication. Remember you would have to answer within 60 seconds to stay in this arcade game. Being an expert in the four math operations will help to become proficient. Try to find out the right answers of as many questions as you can before your time expires! When you click the play button, you would have three unique and difficult levels to choose from. 
Select any mode and have fun in this one of the best cool mathematics fun game! You can see which operation you are currently playing by looking at the top of the screen. Four different answers are given right below those options.

Challenge your quick thinking abilities to find out the right answers and move further! Feel free to click the appropriate button to get the help in case if you feel that you are stuck in the game! There are only 5 times you can use this feature. You will lose your game if your time is over. Check out more popular titles from the category of math games and have fun with your friends for free, no download required!
